---
---

<section id="about" class="py-24 bg-cream">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-5">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      <!-- Image -->
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden aspect-[4/5]">
          <img
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1601979031925-424e53b6caaa?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80"
            alt="Happy dog after grooming at Put Together Pooch"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>
        <!-- Accent badge -->
        <div class="absolute -bottom-5 -right-5 bg-gold text-bark rounded-2xl px-6 py-4 shadow-lg">
          <p class="text-3xl font-bold leading-none">13+</p>
          <p class="text-sm font-medium mt-1">Years in Denver</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Text -->
      <div>
        <p class="text-forest text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Our Story</p>
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-bark leading-tight mb-6">
          A groomer who knows your dog's name.
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-muted text-lg leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            Put Together Pooch has been part of Denver's City Park West neighborhood since June 2012. We believe grooming should be a calm, personal experience, not a conveyor belt.
          </p>
          <p>
            When you bring your dog to us, you'll always know exactly who's doing the grooming. We take time to understand your dog's temperament, coat needs, and quirks so every visit is a good one.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap gap-6">
          <div>
            <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-forest">Tue–Sat</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-muted mt-0.5">10am – 6pm</p>
          </div>
          <div class="w-px bg-cream-dark"></div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-forest">Sunday</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-muted mt-0.5">12pm – 6pm</p>
          </div>
          <div class="w-px bg-cream-dark"></div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-forest">Monday</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-muted mt-0.5">Closed</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
